{"tid":1629631,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[警世] 神獸顯靈之餘要不忘初衷","createTime":"2019-10-06T10:02:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T11:02:47.000Z","uid":294580,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"baa64c2c5e55ab7a03035799d252ef13e2200791","tid":1629631,"uid":294580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:02:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">利申：唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">今日有條藍絲遊行嗰陣揸車出黎撞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗱係佢仆街先 抵撚佢死 我同意<br />\n咁班手足就捉佢落車鶳佢 我同意<br />\n但係打到佢仆街 冇還擊之力 之後都唔停手 繼續踏佢 打佢個頭 流撚晒血 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">畫面就唔多好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span> <br />\n<br />\n利申 我覺得打斷佢手手腳腳都唔過分 但係打死佢 我就覺得違反咗我地初衷 我地唔係要發泄同班死黑警一樣呀！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打到佢還唔到手 下次出唔到黎撞人就好啦 綁起佢係條柱都冇撚問題呀 <br />\n </span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">但唔好打死人</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我知呢條冚家鏟撞到我地手足昏迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我屌佢老母呀！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係大家都要記住 我地係義士 唔係黑警黑社會福建幫 要適可而止呀 </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割席 不分化 <br />\n光復香港 時代革命 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">實會有人衝出黎話我五毛分化 </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 只係希望大家係屌我之前 記得我地既初心 記得我地同黑警既分別 千祈唔好做咗我地痛恨既黑警 做返佢地無差別 冇人性咁做既野</span>"},{"pid":"ce1d250cf0760c60a874f0ca9f30fae8f55956cb","tid":1629631,"uid":294580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:02:46.000Z","msg":"自推 1"},{"pid":"528b7effbf44c16b280aa2a9251571c00acbaf0c","tid":1629631,"uid":294580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:03:04.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"ad4ee681c362e6c966f1ccf6511e7ccfeea1d0fc","tid":1629631,"uid":131852,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:03:13.000Z","msg":"試下打手腳打關節<br />\n有效好多"},{"pid":"4dc12e292bfd9720253d34934737a6d97fc36130","tid":1629631,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:03:44.000Z","msg":"唔好死人"},{"pid":"84772d9c6d67331bd4924a6a8f82b564c3486c56","tid":1629631,"uid":182653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:04:20.000Z","msg":"好多野示威者都快速進步<br />\n係呢樣一直都冇改善<br />\n針對手腳啦"},{"pid":"ed14ff5827cc57c49b7e5e81a5b8e32038c0a5b3","tid":1629631,"uid":50502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:04:43.000Z","msg":"講左好多次 鶳完對腳仲行到既 鶳行動係失敗左"},{"pid":"b10c0f93c1153a098f859bfe9987f30444f65662","tid":1629631,"uid":47309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"baa64c2c5e55ab7a03035799d252ef13e2200791","tid":1629631,"uid":294580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:02:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">利申：唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">今日有條藍絲遊行嗰陣揸車出黎撞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗱係佢仆街先 抵撚佢死 我同意<br />\n咁班手足就捉佢落車鶳佢 我同意<br />\n但係打到佢仆街 冇還擊之力 之後都唔停手 繼續踏佢 打佢個頭 流撚晒血 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">畫面就唔多好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></